00:23:33,500 --> 00:23:37,290
我告诉过你  不过你仔细听了吗
I did tell you... but did you listen?

353
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:53,150
对你来说  说句"我不知道"有多困难
How hard do you find it, having to say "I don't know"?

354
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:57,970
- 我不知道  - 很聪明啊  真聪明
- I don't know. - That's clever, very clever, awfully clever.

355
00:23:57,970 --> 00:24:01,310
说起聪明  你跟你那些小朋友说了吗
Speaking of clever, have you told your little friends yet?

356
00:24:01,310 --> 00:24:02,090
说什么
Told them what?

357
00:24:02,090 --> 00:24:05,480
- 为何我闯入那些地方却空手而回  - 没有
- Why I broke into all those places and never took anything? - No.

358
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:07,310
- 但你明白  - 当然
- But you understand? - Obviously.

359
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,130
那请说吧
Off you go, then.

360
00:24:08,130 --> 00:24:09,630
你自己也知道  我还说什么
You want me to tell you what you already know?

361
00:24:09,630 --> 00:24:11,560
不  我要你证明你知道
No, I want you to prove that you know it.

362
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:15,110
- 什么都不拿是因为你不需要  - 好
- You didn't take anything because you don't need to. - Good.

363
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:16,940
你再也不用拿任何东西了
You'll never need to take anything ever again.

364
00:24:16,940 --> 00:24:18,660
很好  因为什么
Very good, because?

365
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:22,750
因为英格兰银行  伦敦塔和本顿维尔监狱
Because nothing in the Bank of England, the Tower of London

366
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:25,570
里面没有东西能比上你手里那个
or Pentonville Prison could possibly match the value of the key

367
00:24:25,570 --> 00:24:26,710
能让你闯入其中的钥匙
that could get you into all three.

368
00:24:26,710 --> 00:24:28,950
任何地方的任何门我都打得开
I can open any door anywhere

369
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:31,700
只要几行计算机代码就行
with a few tiny lines of computer code.

370
00:24:31,700 --> 00:24:34,800
什么私人银行账户都是胡扯  全属于我
No such thing as a private bank account now, they're all mine.

371
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:38,510
已经没有秘密了  我掌控着秘密
No such thing as secrecy, I own secrecy.

372
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:40,380
核武器编码
Nuclear codes?

373
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:42,900
我随随便便就能炸了北约
I could blow up NATO in alphabetical order.

374
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:47,250
满世界都是封锁的房间  有钥匙便是国王
In a world of locked rooms, the man with the key is king.

375
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:51,440
亲爱的  你真该看看我戴王冠的样子
And honey, you should see me in a crown.

376
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:54,470
你是利用审讯宣传自己
You were advertising all through the trial,

377
00:24:54,470 --> 00:24:56,620
给世人展现你的能耐
you were showing the world what you can do.

378
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:57,900
你也帮了我
And you were helping.

379
00:24:58,560 --> 00:25:02,200
客户可多了  自由政府  情报组织
Big client list... rogue governments, intelligence communities,

380
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,670
恐怖组织
terrorist cells.

381
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:05,950
他们都想要我
They all want me.

382
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:08,600
转眼我就成了万人迷
Suddenly, I'm Mr Sex.

383
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,650
如果你能进入任何银行
If you can break any bank,

384
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,700
你还在乎什么最高价竞买人
what do you care about the highest bidder?

385
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,940
我不在乎  我就是爱看他们抢破头的样
I don't, I just like to watch them all competing.

386
00:25:14,940 --> 00:25:18,810
"爸爸最爱的是我"  凡人真可爱
"Daddy loves me the best." Aren't ordinary people adorable?

387
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:21,570
反正你有约翰了
Well, you know, you've got John.

388
00:25:22,050 --> 00:25:24,180
我也该找个同居男友才对
I should get myself a live- in one.

389
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,940
- 你为什么要这么做  - 肯定很有趣
- Why are you doing all of this? - It must be so funny.

390
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:29,480
你并不真的想要金钱或权力
You don't want money or power, not really.

391
00:25:30,090 --> 00:25:32,900
到底为了什么
What is it all for?

392
00:25:32,900 --> 00:25:35,090
我想解决那个问题
I want to solve the problem.

393
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:38,350
我们的问题
Our problem.

394
00:25:38,780 --> 00:25:40,430
最后的谜题
The final problem.

395
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:47,320
就要开始了  夏洛克  坠落
It's going to start very soon, Sherlock... the fall.

396
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:47,320
fall[坠落]同有瀑布之意  在这里双关

397
00:25:48,890 --> 00:25:52,110
不过别怕  坠落跟飞翔一样
But don't be scared, falling is just like flying,

398
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:54,600
不过下场只有死亡而已
except there's a more permanent destination.

399
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:03,710
我不喜欢谜语
Never liked riddles.

400
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:08,600
学着喜欢
Learn to.

401
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:12,380
因为我欠你一次坠落  夏洛克
Because I owe you a fall, Sherlock.

402
00:26:14,460 --> 00:26:18,710
我  欠  你
I... owe... you.

403
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,190
莫里亚蒂无罪释放  中央法庭惊人的判决

404
00:26:46,190 --> 00:26:47,230
惊天罪犯

405
00:26:47,230 --> 00:26:48,660
如何

406
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,130
他如何脱罪

407
00:26:50,820 --> 00:26:51,580
莫里亚蒂消失了

408
00:26:51,580 --> 00:26:54,640
莱辛巴赫英雄接下来又如何

409
00:26:55,690 --> 00:26:58,550
两个月后

410
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,350
您的卡出现问题

411
00:27:09,250 --> 00:27:10,350
请稍等

412
00:27:10,950 --> 00:27:14,900
感谢您的耐心

413
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:14,900
约翰

414
00:27:36,170 --> 00:27:38,900
第欧根尼俱乐部

415
00:27:50,170 --> 00:27:53,410
打扰下  我找麦考夫・福尔摩斯
Excuse me, I'm looking for Mycroft Holmes?

416
00:27:56,260 --> 00:27:58,170
请问他在不在
Would you happen to know if he's around at all?

417
00:27:59,020 --> 00:27:59,990
你听不见我说话吗
Can you not hear me?

418
00:28:00,990 --> 00:28:03,570
好吧  有人知道吗
Yes, all right. Anyone?

419
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,720
谁知道...
Anyone at all know...

420
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:08,850
麦考夫・福尔摩斯在哪  有人叫我在这等他
where Mycroft Holmes is, I've been asked to meet him here?

421
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,650
没人理我  好吧
No takers, right.

422
00:28:10,650 --> 00:28:12,460
我是透明的吗  你们看得见我么
Am I invisible, can you actually see me?

423
00:28:13,980 --> 00:28:16,240
多谢两位  有人叫我来找麦考夫・福尔摩斯
Thanks, gents. I've been asked to meet Mycroft Holmes.

424
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,320
搞什么飞机
What the hell?!

425
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:22,840
传统嘛  约翰  传统界定了我们
Tradition, John, our traditions define us.

426
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:25,000
不准讲话算哪门子传统
So total silence is traditional, is it?

427
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,420
连句"把糖递给我"都不能说吗
You can't even say pass the sugar?

428
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,600
大半个外交部门
Three- quarters of the diplomatic service

429
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:31,860
和半个政府议会要员在一起喝茶
and half the government front bench all sharing one tea trolley,

430
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:33,760
这对大家都好  相信我
it's for the best, believe me.

431
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:37,740
我们可不想重演1972年的事
We don't want a repeat of... 1972.

432
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:37,740
血色星期天事件

433
00:28:38,340 --> 00:28:41,120
- 不过在这可以说话  - 你看这个
- But we can talk in here. - You read this stuff?

434
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,150
挺有意思
Caught my eye.

435
00:28:43,130 --> 00:28:46,300
周六他们要爆个猛料
Saturday, they're doing a big expose.

436
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:48,860
真好奇她从哪拿到的这些信息
I'd love to know where she got her information.

437
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:51,900
一个叫布鲁克的人  认识么
Someone called Brook. Recognise the name?

438
00:28:52,210 --> 00:28:53,420
可能是校友吧
School friend, maybe?

439
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:56,070
夏洛克的校友
Of Sherlock's?

440
00:28:57,450 --> 00:28:59,500
不过这不是我叫你来的原因
But that's not why I asked you here.

441
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:08,160
- 这谁  - 不认识吗
- Who's that? - Don't know?

442
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:10,110
- 不认识  - 没见过他
- No. - Never seen his face before?

443
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:13,560
他刚住到贝克街  就和你隔了两户人家
He's taken a flat in Baker Street, two doors down from you.

444
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:16,320
我正想拜访下邻居呢
I was thinking of doing a drinks thing for the neighbours.

445
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:18,100
我看还是算了
I'm not sure you'll want to.

446
00:29:19,050 --> 00:29:23,340
苏莱曼尼  阿尔巴尼亚职业杀手
Sulejmani, Albanian hit squad, expertly trained killer,

447
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:25,910
就住在离你家不到20尺的地方
living less than 20 feet from your front door.

448
00:29:25,910 --> 00:29:28,610
那地段很好  坐地铁很方便
Well, it's a great location. Jubilee line's handy.

449
00:29:28,610 --> 00:29:29,930
- 约翰  - 这跟我有什么关系
- John... - What's it got to do with me?

450
00:29:29,970 --> 00:29:32,480
德琴科・卢德米拉
Dyachenko Ludmila.

451
00:29:35,670 --> 00:29:38,110
- 我好像见过她  - 俄国杀手
- Actually, I think I have seen her. - Russian killer.

452
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:39,920
住你家对面
She's taken the flat opposite.

453
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:41,770
好吧
Ok.

454
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:43,950
我有点明白你的意思了
I'm sensing a pattern here.

455
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:47,620
其实  四个国际顶级刺客都搬到了
In fact, four top international assassins relocate

456
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:50,660
221B附近
to within spitting distance of 221b.

457
00:29:51,950 --> 00:29:53,520
有什么想告诉我的么
Anything you'd care to share with me?

458
00:29:54,770 --> 00:29:55,710
我该搬家了吗
I'm moving?

459
00:29:56,380 --> 00:29:58,680
不难猜到他们的共同之处
It's not hard to guess the common denominator, is it?

460
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,190
你觉得是莫里亚蒂安排的吗
You think this is Moriarty?

461
00:30:00,970 --> 00:30:02,710
他跟夏洛克说他一定会回来
He promised Sherlock he'd come back.

462
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:04,520
如果这是莫里亚蒂的杰作  我们早就死了
If this was Moriarty, we'd be dead already.

463
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:06,810
如果不是莫里亚蒂  那又是谁
If not Moriarty, then who?

464
00:30:08,810 --> 00:30:11,930
你既然这么担心他  怎么不去找夏洛克谈谈
Why don't you talk to Sherlock, if you're so concerned about him?

465
00:30:12,650 --> 00:30:14,790
天呐  别说了
God, don't tell me.

466
00:30:15,690 --> 00:30:17,360
我们之间有太多事  约翰
Too much history between us, John.

467
00:30:17,700 --> 00:30:20,410
旧账  愤恨
Old scores, resentments.

468
00:30:20,410 --> 00:30:23,380
偷走了他的蓝精灵  还是弄坏了他的机动战士
Nicked all his Smurfs? Broke his Action Man?

469
00:30:28,240 --> 00:30:29,040
看完了
Finished.

470
00:30:30,170 --> 00:30:32,060
我们都知道要发生什么  约翰
We both know what's coming, John.

471
00:30:32,350 --> 00:30:36,350
莫里亚蒂不会罢休  他发誓要干掉他唯一的敌手
Moriarty is obsessed, he's sworn to destroy his only rival.

472
00:30:36,350 --> 00:30:38,080
所以你要我去照看你弟弟
So you want me to watch out for your brother

473
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:40,150
就因为他不会接受你的帮助
because he won't accept your help?

474
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:42,720
希望不会太麻烦你
If it's not too much trouble?

475
00:31:25,860 --> 00:31:28,260
- 借过  - 抱歉
- Excuse me. - Sorry.

476
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:37,170
夏洛克  有件怪事...
Sherlock, something weird...

477
00:31:37,670 --> 00:31:38,310
怎么回事
What's going on?

478
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:41,340
- 绑架案  - 驻美大使路法斯・布卢尔
- Kidnapping. - Rufus Bruhl. The ambassador to the US.

479
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:42,440
他不是在华盛顿吗
He's in Washington, isn't he?

480
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:43,630
不是他  是他的孩子
Not him, his children.

481
00:31:43,630 --> 00:31:45,770
麦斯和克劳黛  一个七岁  一个九岁
Max and Claudette, age seven and nine.

482
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:48,440
- 他们在圣艾尔代茨  - 萨里郡的豪华寄宿学校
- They're at St Aldates. - Posh boarding place in Surrey.

483
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:50,640
学校放假  其他寄宿生都回家了
School broke up, all the boarders went home.

484
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,490
只有几个孩子留校  就包括他俩
Just a few kids remained, including those two.

485
00:31:52,490 --> 00:31:53,670
两个孩子不见了
The kids have vanished.

486
00:31:53,670 --> 00:31:55,510
大使亲自指名找你
The ambassador's asked for you personally.

487
00:31:56,100 --> 00:31:57,670
莱辛巴赫英雄
The Reichenbach hero.

488
00:32:00,470 --> 00:32:02,650
跟名人一起办案真不错啊
Isn't it great to be working with a celebrity?

489
00:32:12,810 --> 00:32:15,470
应该很快就能放你走了  谢谢
We shouldn't need to keep you for much longer. Thank you.

490
00:32:16,570 --> 00:32:20,120
- 没事了  - 麦肯齐小姐是舍监  温柔点
- It's all right. - Miss MacKenzie, House Mistress. Go easy.

491
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,790
麦肯齐小姐  你负责学生的安全
Miss MacKenzie, you're in charge of pupil welfare,

492
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:24,540
可昨晚却有人轻易闯入
yet you left this place wide open last night.

493
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:26,360
你是白痴  喝醉了  还是同伙
What are you, an idiot, a drunk or a criminal?!

494
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,560
立刻  迅速  回答我
Now, quickly, tell me!

495
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:30,880
门窗都关好了
All the doors and the windows were properly bolted.

496
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:34,150
昨晚没有任何人  包括我都没进过他们的房间
No- one, not even me, went into their room last night.

497
00:32:34,150 --> 00:32:35,580
你得相信我
You have to believe me!

498
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:37,260
我相信  我就是想让你快点说
I do, I just wanted you to speak quickly.

499
00:32:37,260 --> 00:32:39,420
麦肯齐小姐需要个口袋呼吸
Miss MacKenzie will need to breath into a bag now.

500
00:32:47,380 --> 00:32:48,650
每学期六千块
Six grand a term,

501
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:50,750
居然还不能保证孩子的安全
you'd expect them to keep the kids safe for you.

502
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,690
你说其他的孩子都放假走了
You said the other kids had all left on their holidays.

503
00:32:53,690 --> 00:32:55,810
只有他们俩还住在这层楼上
They were the only two sleeping on this floor.

504
00:32:55,810 --> 00:32:57,820
完全没有强行闯入的迹象
There's absolutely no sign of a break- in.

505
00:32:57,820 --> 00:33:00,550
闯入者肯定是藏在什么地方了
The intruder must have been hidden inside some place.

506
00:33:09,620 --> 00:33:11,630
格林童话

507
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:15,880
带我去哥哥的房间
Show me where the brother slept.

508
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:31,520
小男孩每晚都睡在这儿
The boy sleeps there every night.

509
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:35,300
盯着从走廊投进来的唯一光线
Gazing at the only light source outside in the corridor.

510
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:37,910
他会认出每个人的形态和轮廓
He'd recognise every shape, every outline,

511
00:33:37,910 --> 00:33:40,090
每一个走到门前的人的剪影
the silhouette of everyone who came to the door.

512
00:33:40,520 --> 00:33:41,620
那又如何
OK, so?

513
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:43,740
那样  如果有一个他没见过的人走到门前
So if someone approaches the door who he doesn't recognise,

514
00:33:43,740 --> 00:33:47,100
就知道是闯入者  或许他都能看到武器的轮廓
an intruder, maybe he can even see the outline of a weapon.

515
00:33:51,740 --> 00:33:52,780
他会怎么做
What would he do?

516
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:55,760
在他们闯进来之前珍贵的几秒钟内
In the precious few seconds before they came into the room,

517
00:33:56,470 --> 00:33:58,410
他如果没有大声呼救  会怎么做
how would he use them if not to cry out?

518
00:33:59,570 --> 00:34:01,950
这个小男孩  就是这个小男孩
This little boy, this particular little boy,

519
00:34:01,950 --> 00:34:05,190
他读了那么多间谍小说  他会怎么做
who reads all of those spy books, what would he do?

520
00:34:05,490 --> 00:34:06,490
留下什么标记吗
He'd leave a sign?

521
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:20,290
叫安德森来
Get Anderson!

522
00:34:22,600 --> 00:34:26,310
帮帮我们

523
00:34:22,870 --> 00:34:23,810
