这下没人来保释我们了
There's no- one to bail us.

893
00:54:40,020 --> 00:54:42,790
我更倾向于现在就大胆逃跑
I was thinking more about our imminent and daring escape.

894
00:54:43,440 --> 00:54:45,710
- 所有单位到27区  - 什么
- All units to 27. - What?

895
00:54:45,710 --> 00:54:47,410
所有单位到2
All units to 2...

896
00:54:51,860 --> 00:54:54,500
女士们  先生们  请你们趴下好吗
Ladies and gentlemen, will you all please get on your knees?

897
00:54:56,570 --> 00:54:59,200
- 最好现在就趴下  - 照他说的做
- NOW would be good! - Do as he says!

898
00:55:00,750 --> 00:55:03,110
提醒你们一声  枪是他夺的
Just so you're aware, the gun is his idea,

899
00:55:03,110 --> 00:55:04,850
我就是个  你知道
I'm just a... you know.

900
00:55:05,150 --> 00:55:05,680
我的人质
My hostage.

901
00:55:05,680 --> 00:55:07,640
人质  没错  这个可以有
Hostage, yes, that works.

902
00:55:07,970 --> 00:55:09,060
这个可以有
That works.

903
00:55:09,060 --> 00:55:10,170
现在怎么办
So what now?

904
00:55:10,740 --> 00:55:14,520
如莫里亚蒂所愿  做个逃犯  跑
Doing what Moriarty wants, becoming a fugitive. Run!

905
00:55:18,100 --> 00:55:19,810
追上他  雷斯垂德
Get after him, Lestrade!

906
00:55:22,620 --> 00:55:23,510
抓紧我的手
Take my hand.

907
00:55:25,910 --> 00:55:27,540
这下肯定要被人闲话了
Now people will definitely talk.

908
00:55:27,730 --> 00:55:29,220
- 枪掉了  - 别管了
- The gun! - Leave it!

909
00:55:36,130 --> 00:55:37,400
夏洛克  等等
Sherlock, wait!

910
00:55:39,170 --> 00:55:41,730
我们得协调一致才行
We're going to need to coordinate.

911
00:55:42,870 --> 00:55:45,160
往右边去  往你右边去
Go to your right. Go to your right.

912
00:55:49,250 --> 00:55:50,650
每个人都宁可信其有
Everybody wants to believe it,

913
00:55:50,650 --> 00:55:51,720
这就是其高明之处
that's what makes it so clever.

914
00:55:52,350 --> 00:55:54,050
一个比真相更受人青睐的谎言
A lie that's preferable to the truth.

915
00:55:54,370 --> 00:55:55,950
我的演绎法是骗人的
My deductions were a sham.

916
00:55:55,950 --> 00:55:58,550
大家都舒坦了  夏洛克毫无过人之处
No- one feels inadequate, Sherlock's an ordinary man.

917
