现在真不是打亲情牌的好时机
Big family reconciliation, now's not really the moment.

919
00:56:06,690 --> 00:56:07,960
夏洛克
Sherlock...

920
00:56:08,100 --> 00:56:08,970
有人跟来了
we're being followed.

921
