那人不是警察
That's not the police,

923
00:56:11,160 --> 00:56:12,950
是咱们贝克街上的新邻居
it's one of my new neighbours from Baker Street.

924
00:56:13,690 --> 00:56:15,190
看他能不能给我们答案
Let's see if he can give us some answers.

925
00:56:21,190 --> 00:56:22,590
我们去哪儿
Where are we going?

926
