他公开售卖
He's selling it.

934
00:56:50,670 --> 00:56:52,410
闯进伦敦塔的程序
The programme he used to break into the Tower.

935
00:56:54,460 --> 00:56:56,530
他是在来的时候动的手脚
He planted it when he came around.

936
00:57:12,990 --> 00:57:14,070
它可以扭转局面
It's a game- changer.

937
00:57:15,180 --> 00:57:18,070
它是把钥匙  能攻破任何系统
It's a key, it can break into any system

938
00:57:18,070 --> 00:57:19,340
此时此刻就在我们公寓
and it's sitting in our flat right now.

939
00:57:19,340 --> 00:57:20,830
所以他留下那个信息
That's why he left that message,

940
00:57:20,830 --> 00:57:23,190
告诉大家该去哪里  "去找夏洛克"
telling everyone where to come, "Get Sherlock!"

941
00:57:23,740 --> 00:57:25,300
我们必须回公寓找到它
We need to get back into the flat and search.

942
00:57:25,680 --> 00:57:27,150
刑事调查局在那守着
CID will be camped out.

943
00:57:27,580 --> 00:57:28,580
为什么栽赃给你
Why plant it on you?

944
00:57:29,460 --> 00:57:31,370
又一个搞坏我名声的歪点子
It's another subtle way of smearing my name,

945
00:57:31,370 --> 00:57:33,200
现在我成了那些罪行的最大嫌疑人
now I'm best pals with all those criminals.

946
00:57:35,460 --> 00:57:36,780
你看过这个吗
Yeah, well, have you seen this?

947
00:57:38,590 --> 00:57:39,540
大爆料
A kiss- and- tell.

948
00:57:39,310 --> 00:57:40,950
夏洛克  骇人听闻的真相
密友理查・布鲁克彻底坦白

949
00:57:39,540 --> 00:57:41,180
一个叫理查・布鲁克的家伙
Some bloke called Rich Brook.

950
00:57:43,410 --> 00:57:44,160
这人是谁
Who is he?

951
00:58:10,950 --> 00:58:12,450
现在发表声明是不是太晚了
Too late to go on the record?

952
00:58:14,200 --> 00:58:16,750
恭喜了  "夏洛克・福尔摩斯的真相"
Congratulations, "The Truth About Sherlock Holmes."

953
00:58:17,610 --> 00:58:20,070
谁都想要的独家  而你搞到了  漂亮
The scoop that everybody wanted and you got it. Bravo!

954
00:58:20,070 --> 00:58:21,530
我给过你机会
I gave you your opportunity.

955
00:58:21,890 --> 00:58:24,000
我本想站在你这边  记得吗
I wanted to be on your side, remember?

956
00:58:24,870 --> 00:58:26,360
你拒绝了我  所以...
You turned me down, so...

957
00:58:26,360 --> 00:58:28,070
然后就有大惊喜  有人爆出猛料
Then lo and behold, someone spills all the beans.

958
00:58:28,070 --> 00:58:30,000
真是心想事成  布鲁克是谁
How utterly convenient. Who is Brook?

959
00:58:31,990 --> 00:58:34,730
说吧  姬蒂  鬼才相信电话爆料
Come on, Kitty, no- one trusts the voice at the end of a phone.

960
00:58:35,270 --> 00:58:37,510
毫无疑问  咖啡馆里碰面
All those little meetings in cafes,

961
00:58:37,510 --> 00:58:38,670
酒店房间里会谈
those sessions in the hotel room

962
00:58:38,670 --> 00:58:40,240
他对着采访机侃侃而谈
when he gabbled into your Dictaphone.

963
00:58:41,110 --> 00:58:42,560
你怎么就相信他了呢
How do you know that you can trust him?

964
00:58:42,820 --> 00:58:45,460
一个揣着圣杯冒出来的家伙
A man turns up with the Holy Grail in his pockets.

965
00:58:45,940 --> 00:58:47,420
他怎么让你信服的呢
What were his credentials?

966
00:58:49,730 --> 00:58:51,390
亲爱的  买不到咖啡粉煮的
Darling, they didn't have any ground coffee,

967
00:58:51,390 --> 00:58:52,630
我就买了普通的
so I just got normal.

968
00:59:02,340 --> 00:59:03,750
你说过他们不可能找到这里来
You said that they wouldn't find me here,

969
00:59:03,750 --> 00:59:05,120
你说过我在这里很安全
you said that I'd be safe here.

970
00:59:05,120 --> 00:59:06,000
你很安全
You are safe.

971
00:59:06,000 --> 00:59:07,010
理查  我是证人
Richard, I'm a witness,

972
00:59:07,010 --> 00:59:08,500
他们不会当着证人的面伤害你
they wouldn't harm you in front of witnesses.

973
00:59:08,500 --> 00:59:10,170
这就是你的爆料人
So that's your source?

974
00:59:10,640 --> 00:59:12,400
莫里亚蒂就是理查・布鲁克
Moriarty is Richard Brook?

975
00:59:12,400 --> 00:59:15,160
他就是理查・布鲁克  不存在莫里亚蒂
Of course he's Richard Brook, there is no Moriarty.

976
00:59:15,710 --> 00:59:16,830
从来就没有这个人
There never has been.

977
