- 你说什么胡话  - 仔细看看他
- What are you talking about? - Look him up.

978
00:59:19,150 --> 00:59:23,860
理查・布鲁克  夏洛克雇来扮演莫里亚蒂的人
Rich Brook, an actor Sherlock Holmes hired to be Moriarty.

979
00:59:29,240 --> 00:59:32,000
华生医生  我知道你是好人
Dr Watson, I know you're a good man,

980
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:34,930
不要  不要伤害我
don't, don't, don't hurt me.

981
00:59:35,160 --> 00:59:37,420
不对  你是莫里亚蒂  他就是莫里亚蒂
No, you are Moriarty! He's Moriarty!

982
00:59:37,420 --> 00:59:39,870
我们见过  记得吗  你想把我炸死
We've met, remember? You were going to blow me up!

983
00:59:40,930 --> 00:59:42,940
对不起  对不起
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

984
00:59:43,230 --> 00:59:45,990
他出钱雇我  而我需要活儿
He paid me, I needed the work.

985
00:59:45,990 --> 00:59:47,350
我是个演员  我失业了
I'm an actor, I was out of work.

986
00:59:47,350 --> 00:59:49,060
夏洛克  你最好解释一下
Sherlock, you'd better explain,

987
00:59:49,060 --> 00:59:50,170
我完全搞不懂了
because I am not getting this.

988
00:59:50,170 --> 00:59:53,150
我来解释吧  白纸黑字
I'll be doing the explaining, in print.

989
00:59:53,380 --> 00:59:55,980
全在这里  板上钉钉的证据
It's all here, conclusive proof.

990
00:59:57,420 --> 01:00:00,900
夏洛克是个骗子
他策划了所有的罪案

991
00:59:57,420 --> 01:00:00,900
你虚构出金姆斯・莫里亚蒂  所谓的夙敌
You invented James Moriarty, your nemesis.

992
01:00:00,900 --> 01:00:01,970
虚构出来的
Invented him?!

993
01:00:01,970 --> 01:00:03,800
事实上所有的罪案都是他策划的
He invented all the crimes, actually.

994
01:00:03,800 --> 01:00:06,100
最厉害的是凭空造出一位犯罪大师
And to cap it all, he made up a master villain.

995
01:00:06,410 --> 01:00:08,320
- 这太扯了  - 问他啊
- Don't be ridiculous! - Ask him.

996
01:00:08,320 --> 01:00:10,170
他就在这里  问他啊
He's right here. Just ask him.

997
01:00:10,170 --> 01:00:12,760
- 告诉他  理查  - 得了吧  他上过庭
- Tell him, Richard. - For God's sake, this man was on trial!

998
01:00:12,760 --> 01:00:15,430
没错  就是你付钱让他背黑锅
Yes, and you paid him, pay him to take the rap.

999
01:00:15,430 --> 01:00:17,260
还保证搞定陪审团
Promised you'd rig the jury.

1000
01:00:17,930 --> 01:00:20,800
虽然不是伦敦西区的角色  但我猜钱也不少
Not exactly a West End role, but I'll bet the money was good.

1001
01:00:21,190 --> 01:00:23,310
但也不够多  否则他不会爆料
But not so good he didn't want to sell his story.

1002
01:00:23,310 --> 01:00:26,040
对不起  诚心的  非常抱歉
I am sorry. I am. I am sorry.

1003
01:00:26,530 --> 01:00:28,790
你准备发表的就是这个故事
So this is the story you're going to publish?

1004
01:00:28,790 --> 01:00:30,450
最后的结论就是
The big conclusion of it all,

1005
01:00:30,450 --> 01:00:31,780
莫里亚蒂只是个演员
Moriarty's an actor?

1006
01:00:31,780 --> 01:00:32,790
他心里明白
He knows I am.

1007
01:00:32,790 --> 01:00:34,810
我有证据  有证据  给他们看...
I have proof. I have proof. Show them...

1008
01:00:34,810 --> 01:00:35,780
姬蒂  给他们看看
Kitty, show them something.

1009
01:00:35,780 --> 01:00:36,640
好啊  拿出来我看看
Yeah, show me something.

1010
01:00:42,470 --> 01:00:44,430
我上过电视  是儿童频道
I'm on TV. I'm on kids' TV.

1011
01:00:44,900 --> 01:00:46,080
我讲故事
I'm the story- teller.

1012
01:00:46,340 --> 01:00:47,240
理查・布鲁克

1013
01:00:47,620 --> 01:00:48,860
获奖演员参演热门医疗剧

1014
01:00:50,330 --> 01:00:52,570
我讲故事  出过DVD
I'm the story- teller. It's on DVD.

1015
01:00:58,650 --> 01:00:59,370
理查・布鲁克
简历

1016
01:01:00,020 --> 01:01:00,800
告诉他
Just tell him.

1017
01:01:01,470 --> 01:01:03,080
反正都这样了  不用瞒了
It's all coming out. It's all over.

1018
01:01:03,610 --> 01:01:06,650
告诉他们  说啊  说啊  还瞒什么啊
Just tell them. Just tell them. Tell them! It's all over now!

1019
01:01:06,650 --> 01:01:09,530
不要  别碰我  你休想碰我
No! Don't you touch me! Don't you lay a finger on me!

1020
01:01:09,530 --> 01:01:11,340
你耍够了吧
Stop it now!

1021
01:01:12,070 --> 01:01:14,080
别伤害我  不要让他过来
Don't hurt me! Don't let him get away!

1022
01:01:14,080 --> 01:01:14,990
放过他
Leave him alone!

1023
01:01:20,350 --> 01:01:21,810
不行不行  他还有后援
No, no, no. He'll have back- up.

1024
01:01:21,810 --> 01:01:23,300
你知道吗  夏洛克・福尔摩斯
Do you know what, Sherlock Holmes?

1025
01:01:23,600 --> 01:01:28,670
我现在算是看透你了  你让我恶心
I look at you know and I can read you... and you repel me.

1026
01:01:34,300 --> 01:01:35,270
他真能做到吗
Can he do that?

1027
01:01:35,840 --> 01:01:38,770
彻底改变身份  把你抹黑成罪犯
Completely change his identity, make you the criminal?

1028
01:01:38,770 --> 01:01:39,890
他彻底掌握了我的情况
He's got my whole life story.

1029
01:01:40,330 --> 01:01:42,370
要想兜售一个天大的谎言
That's what you do when you sell a big lie,

1030
01:01:42,790 --> 01:01:44,880
将其包裹在真相之中  看上去无懈可击
you wrap it up in the truth to make it more palatable.

1031
01:01:44,880 --> 01:01:45,940
这只是你的一家之言了
It'll be your word against his.

1032
01:01:46,320 --> 01:01:49,350
他用一天时间在人们脑袋里埋下怀疑的种子
He's been sowing doubt into people's minds for 24 hours.

1033
01:01:50,550 --> 01:01:51,060
再做一件事
There's only one thing

1034
01:01:51,060 --> 01:01:52,750
就能结束这场游戏  那就是...
he needs to do to complete his game and that...

1035
