茉莉  我可能快死了
Molly, I think I'm going to die.

1045
01:02:44,810 --> 01:02:45,700
你需要什么
What do you need?

1046
01:02:45,700 --> 01:02:47,770
如果我不是你所以为的样子
If I wasn't everything that you think I am,

1047
01:02:48,180 --> 01:02:49,680
甚至不是我所以为的样子
everything that I think I am...

1048
01:02:52,140 --> 01:02:53,720
你还愿意帮我吗
would you still want to help me?

1049
01:02:55,440 --> 01:02:56,580
你需要什么
What do you need?

1050
01:03:04,660 --> 01:03:05,500
你
You.

1051
01:03:19,750 --> 01:03:24,320
她真的做了不少功课  那个莱利小姐
She has really done her homework, Miss Riley,

1052
01:03:24,320 --> 01:03:27,390
这些事只有和夏洛克最亲近的人才知道
and it's things that only someone close to Sherlock could know.

1053
01:03:29,970 --> 01:03:32,270
你最近有没有看过你弟弟的通讯录
Have you seen your brother's address book lately?

1054
01:03:33,300 --> 01:03:36,310
只有两个名字  你跟我
Two names... yours and mine...

1055
01:03:36,310 --> 01:03:38,590
而莫里亚蒂不是从我这里得到的
and Moriarty didn't get this stuff from me.

1056
01:03:39,500 --> 01:03:42,420
- 约翰  - 怎么回事  你们什么关系
- John... - So how does it work, your relationship?

1057
01:03:42,420 --> 01:03:45,830
你们是不是偶尔出去喝喝咖啡  你跟金
Do you go out for a coffee now and then, you and Jim?

1058
01:03:46,410 --> 01:03:48,340
你的亲弟弟
Your own brother

1059
01:03:48,340 --> 01:03:54,520
你把他的生平故事都告诉了这个疯子
and you blabbed about his entire life to this maniac.

1060
01:03:56,920 --> 01:03:58,990
我根本没打算...我根本没想过...
I never intend... I never dreamt...

1061
01:03:58,990 --> 01:04:02,880
你当时就是想跟我说这件事吧
This... this is what you were trying to tell me, isn't it?

1062
01:04:02,880 --> 01:04:04,960
"照看好他  因为我犯了个错"
"Watch his back because I've made a mistake."

1063
01:04:10,190 --> 01:04:11,020
你怎么认识他的
How did you meet him?

1064
01:04:14,030 --> 01:04:19,300
他这样的人  我们很了解  尽在掌控之中
People like him, we know about them, we watch them.

1065
01:04:20,840 --> 01:04:22,760
但是金姆斯・莫里亚蒂
But James Moriarty...

1066
01:04:25,300 --> 01:04:28,160
拥有前所未有的犯罪头脑
the most dangerous criminal mind the world has ever seen,

1067
01:04:29,820 --> 01:04:31,840
以及最终极的武器
and, in his pocket, the ultimate weapon.

1068
01:04:32,820 --> 01:04:33,770
程序代码
The key code.

1069
01:04:34,710 --> 01:04:38,060
区区几行程序就能畅通无阻
A few lines of computer code that can unlock any door.

1070
01:04:39,750 --> 01:04:43,670
你绑架他就是为了套出代码
And you abducted him to try and find the key code?

1071
01:04:45,360 --> 01:04:47,050
我们对他审问了数周
Interrogated him for weeks.

1072
01:04:47,900 --> 01:04:50,010
- 结果呢  - 他不合作
- And? - He wouldn't play along.

1073
01:04:51,670 --> 01:04:52,770
他只是坐着
He just sat there

1074
01:04:54,690 --> 01:04:56,190
凝视着黑暗
staring into the darkness.

1075
01:05:00,710 --> 01:05:02,300
唯一能让他开口的是...
The only thing that made him open up...

1076
01:05:07,080 --> 01:05:10,250
我可以让他说话  就一点点
I could get him to talk, just a little.

1077
01:05:13,120 --> 01:05:13,930
可是...
But...

1078
01:05:14,860 --> 01:05:17,210
作为回报  你把夏洛克的故事透露给他
In return you had to offer him Sherlock's life story.

1079
01:05:18,850 --> 01:05:21,030
所以  这个天大的谎言
So, one big lie...

1080
01:05:22,700 --> 01:05:23,930
夏洛克是个骗子
Sherlock's a fraud,

1081
01:05:24,450 --> 01:05:26,800
人们会相信  因为别的部分都是真的
and people will swallow it because the rest of it's true.

1082
01:05:29,410 --> 01:05:32,490
莫里亚蒂想要毁了夏洛克
Moriarty wanted Sherlock destroyed, right,

1083
01:05:32,490 --> 01:05:37,700
而你给他送去了最强力的武器
and you have given him the perfect ammunition.

1084
01:05:44,340 --> 01:05:45,240
约翰
John.

1085
01:05:49,360 --> 01:05:50,390
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

1086
01:05:52,010 --> 01:05:52,760
算了吧
Please!

1087
01:05:54,580 --> 01:05:55,690
转告他  好吗
Tell him, would you?

1088
01:06:08,350 --> 01:06:09,100
我收到你的短信
I got your message.

1089
01:06:09,720 --> 01:06:11,060
程序代码是问题的关键
The computer code is the key to this.

1090
01:06:11,060 --> 01:06:11,860
把它找出来并加以使用
We find it, we can use it.

1091
01:06:11,860 --> 01:06:13,400
用莫里亚蒂的方式击败他
Beat Moriarty in his own game.

1092
01:06:13,540 --> 01:06:14,260
你说使用是什么意思
What do you mean use it?

1093
01:06:14,260 --> 01:06:15,820
他用来编造了一个假身份
He used it to create a false identity

1094
01:06:16,550 --> 01:06:19,230
我们也能篡改记录  销毁理查・布鲁克
so we can break into the records and destroy Richard Brook.

1095
01:06:19,230 --> 01:06:20,790
把金・莫里亚蒂逼回来
Bring back Jim Moriarty again.

1096
01:06:20,790 --> 01:06:22,150
他无罪释放那天
Somewhere in 221b,

1097
01:06:22,150 --> 01:06:24,270
他把代码藏在了221B的某个地方
somewhere on the day of the verdict he left it hidden.

1098
01:06:27,790 --> 01:06:29,880
- 他碰过什么  - 一个苹果  仅此而已
- What did he touch? - An apple, nothing else.

1099
01:06:30,860 --> 01:06:32,080
- 他写了什么吗  - 没有
- Did he write anything down? - No.

1100
01:06:51,750 --> 01:06:54,410
\h过来玩吧
\h\h\h巴茨医院楼顶
夏・福

1101
01:06:54,410 --> 01:06:57,790
顺便
\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h带了你也许想拿回去的东西

1102
01:07:24,940 --> 01:07:25,750
是我  请讲
Yeah, speaking.

1103
01:07:26,960 --> 01:07:27,630
什么
What?

1104
01:07:28,120 --> 01:07:29,690
怎么了  她没事吧
What happened? Is she OK?

1105
01:07:31,150 --> 01:07:33,670
不是吧  好  我这就来
My God! Right, yes, I'm coming.

1106
01:07:34,100 --> 01:07:35,160
- 什么事  - 是医护人员
- What is it? - Paramedics.

1107
01:07:35,160 --> 01:07:36,460
赫德森太太受到了枪击
Mrs Hudson's been shot.

1108
01:07:36,460 --> 01:07:37,190
怎么回事
What? How?

1109
01:07:37,190 --> 01:07:40,540
没准是你引来的那些杀手  天啊
Probably one of the killers you managed to attract. Jesus! Jesus!

1110
01:07:40,540 --> 01:07:41,910
她不行了  夏洛克  走吧
She's dying, Sherlock. Let's go.

1111
01:07:41,910 --> 01:07:42,590
你去  我很忙
You go. I'm busy.

1112
01:07:43,850 --> 01:07:45,840
- 忙  - 思考  我需要思考
- Busy?! - Thinking. I need to think.

1113
01:07:46,150 --> 01:07:48,030
你需要...你一点儿都不关心她吗
You need to...? Doesn't she mean anything to you?

1114
01:07:48,030 --> 01:07:50,370
上回有人碰了碰她  你就差点把他杀了
You once half- killed a man because he laid a finger on her.

1115
01:07:50,370 --> 01:07:52,380
- 她是我房东  - 她快死了
- She's my landlady. - She's dying...

1116
01:07:53,460 --> 01:07:54,570
你太冷血了
you machine!

1117
01:07:54,570 --> 01:07:58,680
活见鬼  你就留在这里吧  随你便
Sod this. Sod this! You stay here if you want, on your own.

1118
01:07:58,680 --> 01:08:00,440
我只有孤独作伴  孤独能保护我
Alone is what I have. Alone protects me.

1119
01:08:00,440 --> 01:08:02,670
不对  保护我们的是朋友
No, friends protect people.

1120
01:08:10,150 --> 01:08:12,350
\h\h\h我在等着你哦
金・莫

1121
01:08:38,730 --> 01:08:39,580
好了
Well...

1122
01:08:41,260 --> 01:08:42,800
终于见面了
here we are at last.

1123
01:08:43,940 --> 01:08:46,000
就我们俩  夏洛克
You and me, Sherlock.

1124
01:08:46,810 --> 01:08:49,370
我们的问题  终极问题
And our problem... the final problem.

1125
01:08:50,400 --> 01:08:52,590
活着
Staying alive!

1126
01:08:54,250 --> 01:08:56,110
无聊透顶吧
It's so boring, isn't it?

1127
01:08:58,420 --> 01:09:01,700
一成不变
It's just staying.

1128
01:09:03,110 --> 01:09:05,600
我这辈子都在找乐子
All my life I've been searching for distractions

1129
01:09:05,940 --> 01:09:08,570
你曾经那么有趣  现在也没意思了
and you were the best distraction and now I don't even have you

1130
01:09:09,040 --> 01:09:10,090
因为我打败了你
because I've beaten you.

1131
01:09:10,860 --> 01:09:11,870
你知道吗
And you know what?

1132
01:09:12,220 --> 01:09:13,510
说到底  太简单了
In the end, it was easy.

1133
01:09:15,550 --> 01:09:16,480
没劲
It was easy.

1134
01:09:16,970 --> 01:09:19,550
我只能回去找普通人玩了
Now I've got to go back to playing with the ordinary people,

1135
01:09:19,890 --> 01:09:22,290
而到头来  你也不过和他们一样是个普通人
and it turns out you're ordinary, just like all of them.

1136
01:09:26,040 --> 01:09:26,760
好吧
Well.

1137
01:09:29,660 --> 01:09:31,860
你是不是开始怀疑我是不是真的了
Did you almost start to wonder if I was real?

1138
01:09:33,450 --> 01:09:34,600
你是不是也被我耍了啊
Did I nearly get you?

1139
01:09:35,400 --> 01:09:37,160
理查・布鲁克
Richard Brook.

1140
01:09:38,140 --> 01:09:41,920
没人看出其中的亮点  但你看出来了
Nobody seems to get the joke, but you do.

1141
01:09:41,920 --> 01:09:43,990
- 当然了  - 真不错
- Of course. - Attaboy.

1142
01:09:43,990 --> 01:09:45,890
理查・布鲁克的德语就是莱辛巴赫
Richard Brook in German is Reichenbach.

1143
01:09:46,600 --> 01:09:49,760
- 那个让我出名的案子  - 只是觉得这样很好玩啦
- The case that made my name. - Just trying to have some fun.

1144
01:09:55,490 --> 01:09:57,780
不错啊  你这也看出来了
Good. You got that too.

1145
01:09:59,960 --> 01:10:01,460
数字一样的节奏
Beats like digits.

1146
01:10:02,530 --> 01:10:06,110
每一拍就是1  其余的都是0
Every beat is a one, every rest is a zero.

1147
01:10:06,410 --> 01:10:07,800
二进制代码
Binary code.

1148
01:10:07,800 --> 01:10:10,630
所以那些杀手都要救我
That's why all those assassins tried to save my life.

1149
01:10:11,410 --> 01:10:13,060
代码就藏在我身上  藏在我脑海里
It was hidden on me, hidden inside my head.

1150
01:10:13,060 --> 01:10:14,880
简单的几行程序代码
A few simple lines of computer code

1151
01:10:14,880 --> 01:10:17,080
就可以破解任何系统
that can break into any system.

1152
01:10:17,180 --> 01:10:21,520
我对那些客户说  最后一名是胆小鬼
Told all my clients, last one to Sherlock is a sissy.

1153
01:10:21,530 --> 01:10:25,360
但现在我都知道了  我能用这个修改记录
But now that it's up here, I can use it to alter all the records.

1154
01:10:27,280 --> 01:10:30,750
我能抹杀理查・布鲁克  弄回金・莫里亚蒂
I can kill Rich Brook and bring back Jim Moriarty.

1155
01:10:33,170 --> 01:10:36,720
不不不  这也太简单了
No, no, no, no, no. This is too easy.

1156
01:10:36,720 --> 01:10:38,380
太简单了
This is too easy.

1157
01:10:38,380 --> 01:10:41,360
根本就没什么代码  笨蛋
There is no key, doofus!

1158
01:10:44,360 --> 01:10:47,860
那些数字毫无意义  一点意义都没有
Those digits are meaningless. They're utterly meaningless.

1159
01:10:48,500 --> 01:10:51,540
你不会真以为几行程序代码
You don't really think a couple of lines of computer code

1160
01:10:51,540 --> 01:10:53,450
就能破解全世界的系统吗
are going to crash the world around our ears?

1161
01:10:53,450 --> 01:10:57,320
我好失望哦  普通人夏洛克
I'm disappointed in you, ordinary Sherlock.

1162
01:10:57,320 --> 01:11:02,450
- 但那个节奏  - 是巴赫的1号协奏曲  谢谢
- But the rhythm... Partita no 1! Thank you, Johann Sebastian Bach.

1163
01:11:03,400 --> 01:11:05,070
- 那你又是怎么...  - 怎么黑进银行
- But then how did you... ? - How did I break into the bank,

1164
01:11:05,070 --> 01:11:06,590
伦敦塔  还有监狱吗
to the Tower, to the prison?

1165
01:11:06,590 --> 01:11:11,100
光天化日下的抢劫  只要有同伙就行啦
Daylight robbery! All it takes is some willing participants.

1166
01:11:11,660 --> 01:11:13,200
好戏开始了哦

1167
01:11:16,800 --> 01:11:19,990
我知道你会上钩  这是你的弱点
I knew you'd fall for it. That's your weakness.

1168
01:11:20,170 --> 01:11:21,730
你总是把事情想得很聪明
You always want everything to be clever.

1169
01:11:21,730 --> 01:11:24,890
我们的游戏能结束了吗  最后一幕
Shall we finish the game? One final act.

1170
01:11:24,890 --> 01:11:28,440
幸好你选了一栋高楼  那样做效果很好
Glad you chose a tall building. Nice way to do it.

1171
01:11:28,780 --> 01:11:30,490
做  做什么
Do it? Do what?

1172
01:11:33,740 --> 01:11:35,070
是啊  当然了
Yes, of course.

1173
01:11:37,310 --> 01:11:38,720
自杀
My suicide.

1174
01:11:38,720 --> 01:11:41,070
天才侦探是个骗子
Genius detective proved to be a fraud.

1175
01:11:41,080 --> 01:11:43,680
我在报纸上看到  肯定是真的
I read it in the paper so it must be true.

1176
01:11:43,860 --> 01:11:45,500
我最爱报纸了
I love newspapers.

1177
01:11:46,430 --> 01:11:47,980
还有童话故事
Fairy tales.

1178
01:11:51,010 --> 01:11:52,940
尤其喜欢黑暗的童话
And pretty grim ones too.

1179
01:12:02,170 --> 01:12:06,570
天啊  约翰  你吓死我了  警察那边没事吧
God, John, you made me jump. Is everything OK with the police?

1180
01:12:06,570 --> 01:12:09,270
夏洛克都解决了吧
Has Sherlock sorted it all out?

1181
01:12:11,960 --> 01:12:13,330
我的天
My God.

1182
01:12:16,740 --> 01:12:17,860
出租车
Taxi!

1183
01:12:19,000 --> 01:12:21,900
出租车  等等  我是警察  算是吧
Taxi! No, no, no. Police... sort of!

1184
01:12:21,900 --> 01:12:24,060
谢了  伙计  太谢谢了
Thanks, mate. Thanks a lot!

1185
01:12:24,570 --> 01:12:27,280
我能证明你伪造了那个假身份
I can prove that you created an entirely false identity.

1186
01:12:27,290 --> 01:12:30,020
你就自杀吧  那样省力多了
Just kill yourself. It's a lot less effort.

1187
01:12:31,970 --> 01:12:33,060
跳啊
Go on.

1188
01:12:34,230 --> 01:12:35,390
为了我
For me.

1189
01:12:36,050 --> 01:12:37,870
好不好啦
Please!

1190
01:12:42,870 --> 01:12:44,190
你疯了
You're insane.

1191
01:12:44,730 --> 01:12:47,090
你刚刚知道吗
You're just getting that now? Wo- wo- wo!

1192
01:12:47,750 --> 01:12:48,870
好吧
Ok.

1193
01:12:50,840 --> 01:12:52,950
我再给你点动力
Let me give you a little extra incentive.

1194
01:12:53,790 --> 01:12:56,190
要是你不跳  你朋友就会死
Your friends will die if you don't.

1195
01:12:57,700 --> 01:13:01,180
- 约翰  - 不止是约翰  还有
- John? - Not just John. Everyone.

1196
01:13:02,000 --> 01:13:03,800
- 赫德森太太  - 还有
- Mrs Hudson? - Everyone.

1197
01:13:04,690 --> 01:13:10,640
- 雷斯垂德  - 三发子弹  三个杀手  三个死者
- Lestrade? - Three bullets, three gunmen, three victims.

1198
01:13:10,640 --> 01:13:12,970
没有人能阻止他们了
There's no stopping them now...

1199
01:13:15,250 --> 01:13:17,450
除非他们看到你跳楼
unless my people see you jump.

1200
01:13:25,470 --> 01:13:28,810
尽管逮捕我  折磨我好了
You can have me arrested, you can torture me,

1201
01:13:28,810 --> 01:13:30,860
你想拿我怎么样随便你
you can do anything you like with me,

1202
01:13:30,860 --> 01:13:33,670
但没什么能阻止他们扣下扳机
but nothing's going to prevent them from pulling the trigger.

1203
01:13:33,710 --> 01:13:37,360
你在这世上唯一的三个朋友死定了
Your only three friends in the world will die unless...

1204
01:13:37,360 --> 01:13:40,880
- 除非  - 我自杀  成就你的故事
- Unless... - I kill myself and complete your story.

1205
01:13:42,150 --> 01:13:44,020
你得承认  这样更吸引人
You've got to admit, that's sexier.

1206
01:13:44,790 --> 01:13:48,930
- 我声名狼藉地死去  - 当然了  这才是重点
- And I die in disgrace. - Of course. That's the point of this.

1207
01:13:50,740 --> 01:13:52,370
你现在有观众了哦
You've got an audience now.

1208
01:13:54,210 --> 01:13:55,350
请吧
Off you pop.

1209
01:13:57,600 --> 01:13:58,740
跳吧
Go on.

1210
01:14:00,780 --> 01:14:02,500
我告诉过你故事的结局
I told you how this ends.

1211
01:14:05,970 --> 01:14:07,100
只有你死
Your death is the only thing

1212
01:14:07,100 --> 01:14:09,150
杀手才会收手
that's going to call off the killers.

1213
01:14:09,630 --> 01:14:11,580
我肯定不会这么做
I'm certainly not going to do it.

1214
01:14:13,580 --> 01:14:16,760
你能给我点时间吗
Would you give me one moment, please?

1215
01:14:18,130 --> 01:14:19,770
让我一个人待会
One moment of privacy.

1216
01:14:20,980 --> 01:14:22,110
拜托了
Please.

1217
01:14:25,040 --> 01:14:26,250
当然可以
